Description.enUS: Subversion specialist. Able to manipulate battlefield conditions. Can use the Dark Swarm ability. Can be upgraded to use Consume and Plague.

Creates a micro-organism cloud preventing all incoming ranged projectile damage for 45 seconds.
Melee and Pierce type weapons bypass the cloud
Damage from Spells and Splash is not prevented
